    <item>
      <title>力拓拟以 33 亿美元收购 Arcadium Litium 公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/rio-tinto-confirms-it-s-made-an-approach-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-m1y5cwtw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[双方周一表示，力拓集团 (Rio Tinto Group) 已对 Arcadium Lithium Plc 发出收购要约，确认了这一最新收购提议。目前，该行业正将注意力重新转向增长，各大矿业公司都在竞相增加对能源过渡金属的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/rio-tinto-confirms-it-s-made-an-approach-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-m1y5cwtw</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风米尔顿横扫墨西哥湾，直逼佛罗里达州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/florida-faces-deadly-tropical-threat-in-hurricane-helene-s-wake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风米尔顿正向佛罗里达州前进，强度可能达到四级，并可能引发七年来最大规模的撤离，因为它的目标是该州的墨西哥湾沿岸和坦帕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/florida-faces-deadly-tropical-threat-in-hurricane-helene-s-wake</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 12:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
